# 1. High-Level Product

## Purpose

The project is an **Interior Design Cost Estimation Calculator** for WordPress.

Its goal is:

* Generate an estimated interior quotation
* Allow customers to configure their home
* Estimate pricing dynamically
* Capture lead information
* Produce a quotation/PDF
* Store everything in WordPress Admin

This is **not a simple calculator**.

It is a

> Guided Quote Builder + Dynamic Pricing Engine + Lead Generation System

similar in concept to professional WordPress estimate builders. ([WordPress.org][1])

