# Dynamic Pricing Logic

Although the pricing screen is not shown, the collected information strongly indicates the calculator is intended to apply configurable pricing rules rather than hard-coded values. A likely structure is:

```
Room Base Cost

+

Room Quantity

+

Addon Costs

+

Package Multiplier

↓

Grand Total
```

This follows the standard architecture used by configurable WordPress estimation plugins. ([WordPress.org][1])

